text: Prikaspiysky () is a rural locality (a settlement) and the administrative center of Prikaspiysky Selsoviet, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 1,597 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 77 km from Astrakhan, 110 km from Narimanov. == References == Category:Rural localities in Narimanovsky District
title: Prikaspiysky
